Paper: hep-th/9308111

Date: 1993-08-24

Title: Mechanics as Geometry?

Authors: John M Charap

Comments: 12 pages in Plain Tex, QMW 93-23

Talk given at the Workshop on "Constraint Theory and Quantization Methods";Montepulciano, Italy, June 1993 --- Instead of attempting to give a summary orto identify highlights of the workshop, the history of the development ofanalytical mechanics is outlined, with an emphasis on the themes of \lq naturalmotion' and the variational principle.